日結束。<br />\n<br />\n香港邊城青年不時於台灣舉辦與香港社會運動有關的活動，例如紀錄片《中大保衛戰》及《刑．暴．誌&ndash;記抗爭者》的放映會。"},{"pid":"6c0e35361a267c49bc01957db84289de97ffdca0","tid":2313960,"uid":78243,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T08:11:14.000Z","msg":"十成十係在台支那生做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3df07db952540796c07164a1a8cc6314909ed31","tid":2313960,"uid":332769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T09:12:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50768ad2ee0a1b11d58fe6118e762cc36a892d90","tid":2313960,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6c0e35361a267c49bc01957db84289de97ffdca0","tid":2313960,"uid":78243,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T08:11:14.000Z","msg":"十成十係在台支那生做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T09:21:22.000Z","msg":"見一個斷一個手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af44eb64a058461317964ca9eae3b368bd8cbe1","tid":2313960,"uid":156335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6c0e35361a267c49bc01957db84289de97ffdca0","tid":2313960,"uid":78243,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T08:11:14.000Z","msg":"十成十係在台支那生做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T09:22:35.000Z","msg":"上次潑糞個個咪話收咗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84119e7b49b2b4f7d1f1bb993e203eec1d41fdfe","tid":2313960,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T09:35:12.000Z","msg":"挑戰主辦單位權威<br />\n癱瘓展覽 損害公眾利益<br />\n判監十八個月"}]}